---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../config';
---

<Layout
  title="Únete"
  description="Sumate al Cluster Tecnológico Azul. Completá el formulario y sé parte de la comunidad tecnológica de Azul, Argentina."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Sumate</span>
      <h1>Únete al cluster</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        Completá el formulario y un miembro del equipo se va a poner en contacto con vos.
        El cluster es abierto — nadie queda afuera por su nivel o experiencia.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-body">
    <div class="container page-grid">
      <aside class="form-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3>¿Qué te espera?</h3>
          <ul class="benefit-list">
            <li>
              <span class="benefit-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 0 0-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 0 1 5.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 0 1 9.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Red de contactos local
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="benefit-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Acceso a talleres y capacitaciones
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="benefit-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 0 0 1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 .806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 0 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 0-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 .806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 3.138-3.138z"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Participación en proyectos reales
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="benefit-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 0 1-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Canal de comunicación activo
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="benefit-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 0 0 .95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 0 0-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 0 0-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 0 0-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 0 0 .951-.69l1.519-4.674z"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Mentorías y referentes del sector
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block sidebar-quote">
          <p>"La tecnología no tiene fronteras geográficas. Pero el impacto más profundo ocurre cuando la aplicás en el lugar donde vivís."</p>
          <span>— Equipo fundador, Cluster Tecnológico Azul</span>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="form-container">
        <div id="form-success" class="form-feedback success" hidden role="alert">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3>¡Gracias por sumarte!</h3>
          <p>Recibimos tu solicitud. En breve nos ponemos en contacto con vos.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="form-error" class="form-feedback error" hidden role="alert">
          <p>Ocurrió un error al enviar el formulario. Por favor intentá de nuevo o escribinos a <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <form id="join-form" class="form" novalidate>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="nombre">Nombre y apellido *</label>
              <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Juan Pérez" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="juan@ejemplo.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="rol">¿Cómo te describís? *</label>
              <select id="rol" name="rol" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Seleccioná una opción</option>
                <option value="desarrollador">Desarrollador/a de software</option>
                <option value="diseniador">Diseñador/a UX/UI</option>
                <option value="data">Data / IA / ML</option>
                <option value="emprendedor">Emprendedor/a tech</option>
                <option value="estudiante">Estudiante</option>
                <option value="docente">Docente / investigador/a</option>
                <option value="otro">Otro</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="organizacion">Empresa u organización</label>
              <input type="text" id="organizacion" name="organizacion" placeholder="Opcional" autocomplete="organization" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="mensaje">¿Por qué querés unirte? ¿Qué te gustaría aportar o aprender?</label>
            <textarea id="mensaje" name="mensaje" placeholder="Contanos un poco sobre vos y tus intereses..." rows="5"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="como-conociste">¿Cómo nos conociste?</label>
            <select id="como-conociste" name="como-conociste">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Seleccioná una opción</option>
              <option value="redes">Redes sociales</option>
              <option value="amigo">Un amigo / colega</option>
              <option value="evento">Evento o charla</option>
              <option value="github">GitHub</option>
              <option value="otro">Otro</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit" id="submit-btn">
            <span class="btn-label">Enviar solicitud</span>
            <span class="btn-loading" hidden>
              <svg class="spinner" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"/>
              </svg>
              Enviando...
            </span>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('join-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submit-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
  const successEl = document.getElementById('form-success')!;
  const errorEl = document.getElementById('form-error')!;

  const btnLabel   = submitBtn.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.btn-label');
  const btnLoading = submitBtn.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.btn-loading');

  form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (!form.checkValidity()) { form.reportValidity(); return; }

    submitBtn.disabled = true;
    btnLabel?.setAttribute('hidden', '');
    btnLoading?.removeAttribute('hidden');
    errorEl.hidden = true;

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/unirse', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify(Object.fromEntries(new FormData(form))),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        form.hidden = true;
        successEl.hidden = false;
        successEl.setAttribute('tabindex', '-1');
        successEl.focus();
      } else {
        throw new Error('Error en el servidor');
      }
    } catch {
      errorEl.hidden = false;
      submitBtn.disabled = false;
      btnLabel?.removeAttribute('hidden');
      btnLoading?.setAttribute('hidden', '');
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: calc(68px + 4rem);
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
  }

  .page-hero .section-label {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    color: var(--clr-text-soft);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .page-body {
    padding-block: 4rem;
  }

  .page-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .form-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(68px + 2rem);
  }

  .sidebar-block {
    background: var(--clr-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--clr-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benefit-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .benefit-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--clr-text-soft);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--clr-surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--clr-cyan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sidebar-quote {
    border-color: var(--clr-blue-dim);
    background: rgba(43, 127, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .sidebar-quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--clr-text-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sidebar-quote span {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--clr-muted);
  }

  /* Form */
  .form-container {
    background: var(--clr-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .btn-submit {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
    min-width: 180px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .spinner {
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  /* Feedback */
  .form-feedback {
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-feedback.success {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 200, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 200, 0.3);
    color: var(--clr-cyan);
  }

  .form-feedback.success svg {
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .form-feedback.success h3 {
    color: var(--clr-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-feedback.success p {
    color: var(--clr-text-soft);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .form-feedback.error {
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    color: var(--clr-text-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .page-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .form-sidebar { position: static; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .form-container { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
